:

*Borba* protiv zločina je jako bitna. (The fight against crime is very important.)
*Borićemo* se protiv siromaštva. (We will fight against poverty.)
*Borili* smo se za slobodu. (We fought for freedom.)
*Borbaće* se dok ne postignemo pobedu. (We will fight until we achieve victory.)
*Borben* je bio i pobedio. (He was brave and won.)